        "code": "dialog __main__ do\n  say \"Welcome at Restaurant Sienna 👋\"\n  invoke about\n  show image \"restaurant.jpg\"\nend\n\ndialog __root__ do\n  say \"What can I do for you?\"\nend\n\ndialog trigger: \"about\" do\n  invoke about\nend\n\ndialog about do\n  say \"We serve traditional Italian pizza's.\"\nend",
