        "type": "text",
        "top": 195.5,
        "left": 340,
        "markdown": "[about _ (restaurant | sienna)](https://bml.botsquad.com/?input=Tell+me+about+the+restaurant&locale=en&query=about+_+%28restaurant+%7C+sienna%29)\n\nmatches\n\n\"Tell me about the restaurant\"\n\n\"Can you explain about the place sienna?\""
      },
