        "type": "text",
        "top": 0,
        "left": 340,
        "markdown": "Short form dialog notation"
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "top": 200,
        "left": 340,
        "lang": "text",
        "code": "dialog trigger: @about, do: invoke about"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "top": 340.5,
        "left": 340,
        "markdown": "- comma (,) behind the dialog name\n\n\t- semicolon (:) behind the do\n\n\t- no end"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "top": 0,
        "left": 340,
        "markdown": "Intent, trigger, dialog pattern"
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "top": 72,
        "left": 80,
        "lang": "text",
        "code": "@about   intent(match: [\"about _ (restaurant | sienna)\"])\n@address intent(match: [\"what _ (location | address\", \"where be _ ( you | restaurant)\"])\n@order   intent(match: [\"i _ order\", \"i _ buy\"])\n@close   intent(match: [\"bye | close | stop | goodbye | exit\"])\n\ndialog trigger: @about, do: invoke about\ndialog trigger: @address, do: invoke address\ndialog trigger: @order, do: invoke order\ndialog trigger: @close, do: close\n\ndialog about do\n  say \"We serve traditional Italian pizza's.\"\nend\n\ndialog address do\n  say \"We are located at Joan Muyskenweg 22 in Amsterdam\"\nend\n\ndialog order do\n  ask \"What would you like to order?\"\n  say \"We'll start preparing your #{answer}\"\nend",
        "lineNumbers": "1-4|6-9|11,15,19"
      }
    ]
  },
